{"type": "article", "id": 11099, "title": "Asterisco 书架阅读灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-23T07:06:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052358055irbG9ws3tonFSk7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n\t西班牙设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.cuatrocuatros.com/index.php?/proyectos/corchete/\" target=\"_blank\">Cuatro Cuatros </a>中的两位设计师 Cristina Ródenas 和 Adrián M. Almonacid 与照明公司 LZF 合作，为喜爱阅读的人设计了这款 Asterisco 灯，提供阅读光线的同时，自带的书架让你读书的时候更舒适，让书本以合适的角度竖立，解放双手。木质的灯罩在灯光映射下有趣的花纹显露出来，搭配简洁造型。当然你也可以放平板电脑和手机，做菜的时候用来放菜谱。（<a href=\"http://www.lzf-lamps.com/products/asterisco-mm/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>）\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235804Sjg5H87GfV1UzE30.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.89583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235804sazmDQYfyJWH6ZAU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.9625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235805ZlBovXrdFyPsIjaM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span>\r\n\t\t\t</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n\t\t\r\n<span> </span>\r\n\t\r\n\n\n"}